Author contributions:
R.C.-L., L.H., P.R., and N.R. designed the study. N.R. and R.C.-L. ran
species distribution models. R.C.-L. and P.R. ran Zonation analyses. R.C.-L., N.R., P.R., L.H.,
Y.D.-F., C.D.H., L.R., A.S., and P.v-W. contributed to the discussion of results. R.C.-L. wrote the
manuscript with input from N.R., P.R., L.H., Y.D.-F., C.D.H., L.R, A.S., and P.v-W.
